caption:
art! in reality: i am dealing w friendships & the required drama that follows!!

life is just this like really weird gap between A & B rn so i’m like floating towards B

meanwhile on board to B, i drew this! i was listening to appointments by julien baker & i just drew full body, FINALLY. i know i’ll never get better if i don’t just go out there & let myself make something i KNOW i’ll always see as “ugly”

but we’re here so that’s cool & this is julien, not baker herself, just named after her

summary: [Image Description: A dark skinned character with purple eyes, and long, black hair. They have bald spots on their head, and...
body:
[Image Description: A dark skinned character with purple eyes, and long, black hair. They have bald spots on their head, and they’re wearing a grey hoodie, with the hood pulled up. They’re in front of a purple background. End Description]

Started doodling a character with alopecia areata after watching a video where someone was talking about their experiences with it.

This character doesn’t have a name yet. Got any suggestions?
